text:
29 Seconds of Farcaster ... What did you miss this weekend?

* Drop your answer, no cheating: It was quiet. Let's call it a /crypto-the-game hangover. Plus dan was either skiing or trying to increase qDAU for /snow 

* @bracky was not quiet w/ March Madness & an airdrop. Some funny moments with bracky's saltiness & occasional hallucinations but you can clearly see where bracky is headed: @tldr & bracky 📈 

* Farcaster airdrops are coming (4 this week), which will be interesting. Reminder to verify a Solana wallet. 

* @jacekdegen dropped a new $DEGEN Liquidity Pool w/ beefy; @garrett revealed mechanics for upcoming @higherarrows a Farcaster & /higher spin on Jack Butcher's Checks. And people continued to explore @woj dream feature of Farcaster Earnings. 

* In exciting news, Bert @bertwurst.eth graduated puppy school & celebrated with his first pup cup. 🐾 (headed for top 10 Rewards BTW)

* @adrienne & @nounishprof are on at 11:30 AM EST today w/ all things Purple 💜  & special guest @phil ...join them!

show_title: GM Farcaster ep228 Monday March 24, 2025 with @ phil @ ampsfun
text:
lemon3 is an open source program that uses IPFS and Farcaster to allow decentralized file hosting and sharing.

It's a mini Farcaster client and an IPFS node, and allows uploading and downloading files. Lots of rough edges, this is the mvp, but I'm very excited.

https://blog.vrypan.net/2025/03/23/lemon3-farcaster-ipfs-decentralized-file-sharing/

html.ogDescription: Farcaster+IPFS = Decentralized RSS enclosures and file sharing

text:
𝗖𝗘𝗟𝗘𝗕𝗥𝗔𝗧𝗜𝗡𝗚 𝟮𝟱𝟬 𝗚𝗨𝗘𝗦𝗧𝗦

Friends,

I'm very happy to share that we've reached a milestone for us at /live-the-same.
When we launched the pilot of the interview series with NOE, @noedmb, last October 29th, we couldn't have imagined the impact it would have.

Since then, many people have reached out to the channel, and today, with great joy, I can share with you that the next guest, very special to me, is number 250!

I sincerely thank you for joining me on this journey and for making /live-the-same a space for meeting and genuine connections that make this social network the best of all.

🥂 🫂

Don't miss the next interview. While everyone here at FC knows who it is, never lose the ability to be surprised!
